#: front-page.php:33
msgid "Civic Engagement Tools"
msgstr "Ngāue Fakafonua"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "for the People of Hawaii"
msgstr "maʻa e kakai ʻo Hawaii"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Government information shouldn't require a law degree to navigate. Civi.Me makes it simple to stay informed, show up, and have your voice heard — in plain language, for free."
msgstr "ʻOua ʻe fie maʻu ha tohi lao ke mahino ʻa e fakamatala puleʻanga. ʻOku fakaʻaongaʻi ʻe Civi.Me ke faingofua ʻa e nofo ʻiloʻi, haʻu, mo e fanongo ki hoʻo leʻo — ʻi lea mahino, ta'etotongi."

#: front-page.php:53
msgid "What matters to you?"
msgstr "Ko e hā ʻoku mahuʻinga kiate koe?"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid "Browse meetings"
msgstr "Vakai ki he ngaahi fakataha"

#: front-page.php:167
msgid "The challenge"
msgstr "Ko e faingataʻa"

#: front-page.php:169
msgid "Civic participation should be accessible for all residents"
msgstr "ʻOku totonu ke maʻu ʻe he kakai kotoa pē ha mālohi ki he ngāue fakafonua"

#: front-page.php:172
msgid "People want to be engaged, but the barriers make it feel impossible. We're removing them."
msgstr "ʻOku loto ʻa e kakai ke kau, ka ko e ngaahi tapuni ʻoku fakaʻatā ke ʻikai lava. ʻOku mau toʻo ia."

#: front-page.php:190
msgid "Buried information"
msgstr "Fakamatala kuo fakahūhū"

#: front-page.php:191
msgid "Meeting agendas are buried in PDFs across dozens of county and state websites with no consistent format."
msgstr "Ko e ngaahi lāunga fakataha kuo fakahūhū ʻi he ngaahi PDF ʻi he ngaahi ʻinitaneti fakakaunati mo e puleʻanga ʻo taʻe ha fōma tatau."

#: front-page.php:203
msgid "No timely alerts"
msgstr "ʻIkai ha fakalāloa fakatefito"

#: front-page.php:204
msgid "Residents find out about decisions that affect their neighborhoods after the fact — if at all."
msgstr "ʻOku ʻilo ʻe he kakai ki he ngaahi fili ʻoku ueʻi honau feituʻu hili ʻa e hoko — kapau ʻoku nau ʻilo."

#: front-page.php:219
msgid "Bureaucratic language"
msgstr "Lea fakafakalakalaka"

#: front-page.php:220
msgid "Government documents are written for lawyers, not residents. Plain-language summaries are rare."
msgstr "Ko e ngaahi tohi puleʻanga kuo tohi maʻa e kau lōia, ʻikai maʻa e kakai. Ko e ngaahi fakamālohi lea mahino ʻoku tokolahi."

#: front-page.php:234
msgid "Who are my representatives?"
msgstr "Ko hai hoku kau fakafofonga?"

#: front-page.php:235
msgid "Most residents can't name their city council member, let alone their neighborhood board chair."
msgstr "Ko e kakai tokolahi ʻoku ʻikai te nau lava ke fakahingoa honau kautaha fakasiti, tuku kehe ʻa e ʻeiki nofo ʻo honau vaʻa."

#: front-page.php:254
msgid "Start here"
msgstr "Kamata heni"

#: front-page.php:256
msgid "Tell us what matters to you"
msgstr "Tala mai ko e hā ʻoku mahuʻinga kiate koe"

#: front-page.php:259
msgid "Pick the topics you care about — environment, housing, education, health — and we'll show you the government meetings and councils that handle those issues."
msgstr "Fili ʻa e ngaahi kaveinga ʻoku ke tokanga ki ai — ʻātakai, fale nofo, akoʻanga, moʻui lelei — pea te mau hāʻele koe ki he ngaahi fakataha mo e ngaahi kautaha puleʻanga ʻoku nau fakalelei ʻa e ngaahi meʻa ko ia."

